# Nordpool API

IBEX offers API connectivity of the registered Trading Participants and all companies in contractual relations with IBEX / TP / according to the Power Exchange Operational Rules, State Gazette No. 55 of June 19th, 2020 /PEOR/. Thus  they can effectively integrate their platforms with the existing electronic trading systems, aiming at more convenience, shorter response time and accurate reports.The key benefits of the API connectivity service are:
- Efficient and seamless integration with your internal trading systems, back office systems and operating tools;
- Automated / Robot trading to maximise market opportunities;
- Customised and automated reporting;
- Consolidated, web-based IT solutions.
Only IBEX members, with status “Active” on the IDM (Continuous trading and Intraday auctions mechanisms) and/or DAM according to the PEOR requirements are allowed to use the trading API.
The applicable fees are available in the [IBEX EAD Tariff](https://ibex.bg/download/ibex-ead-tariff-in-force-from-1-1-2026/)on the IBEX website.
